divs: sighting detailsi was putting a bag into my garbage can in my front yard. it was a very clear warm night so i was looking up at all the stars and i looked towards west, i saw some dim light moving but looked away and then back again. the yellowish blurry light was now about 1 mile away and i thought it was a plane and i started to watch it carefully but since i noticed only yellowish lights it couldn't be a plane and it was moving west (wnw) to east (ese). also it was around 1000 to 1500 feet up and then i noticed two separated yellowish\orange blurry illuminated areas and thought about maybe a helicopter. when it was around 600 feet away, i could see two separate groups of 4 yellowish\orange lights bobbing\wiggling around opaque blob with 2 yellowish\orange lights in the rear of the roundish blob. i then realised this wasn't any helicopter and felt creepy and thought about going back inside but i decided to watch. it was moving silently at about 40 miles an hour just alittle farther then my across the street neighbors backyards. i could see clearly an opaque roundish object maybe 40-60 feet wide and 40-50 long with two separate groups of 4 yellowish\orange lights bobbing\wiggling around and 2 wiggling lights in the rear. i watched for the next minute or two moving steadly, silently, towards to south east, until it was to far to see amoung the city lights.
